#

Spicy Chipotle Chicken Bowls

$12.99
600 kcal

Allergens:

None

Dietary Tags:

High-ProteinGluten-FreeLow-Carb

Tags:

ChickenSpicyBowl Meal

Description

A zesty bowl filled with spicy chipotle chicken, fresh veggies, and a creamy avocado sauce.

Ingredients

  • Chicken breast: 1 lb
  • Chipotle sauce: 1/4 cup
  • Bell peppers (mixed colors): 1 cup, sliced
  • Red onion: 1/2, sliced
  • Avocado: 1, diced
  • Cilantro: 1/4 cup, chopped
  • Lime juice: 2 tbsp
  • Olive oil: 2 tbsp
  • Salt: to taste
  • Black pepper: to taste
